  '197f1aca-4879-56f2-9783-85585ad68792',
  '12064006-c71c-5a0b-9338-1c698d60e9d4',
  'Safety Rules',
  '1. **Never decommission multiple nodes simultaneously** unless you''ve calculated safe parallel limit
2. **Always verify cluster health** before decommissioning
3. **Monitor progress actively** - don''t start and walk away
4. **Keep cluster above replication factor** at all times
5. **Test in staging first** for production clusters
6. **Document the plan** before executing
7. **Have rollback plan** (recommission if caught early)',
