  '12064006-c71c-5a0b-9338-1c698d60e9d4',
  'Summary',
  'Decommissioning is a safe, permanent node removal process that:
✅ Moves all replicas to remaining nodes
✅ Maintains cluster availability
✅ Preserves data integrity
✅ Automatically rebalances cluster

**Golden Rule**: Always decommission BEFORE stopping the node process.',
