INSERT INTO chunks (id, skill_id, section_title, content, chunk_index, embedding) VALUES (
  '5ad52e8f-6c4d-52fb-b6b8-fbdd2b4c50e1',
  '1db6956e-7548-5ab7-b308-046fcaca70d3',
  'Monitoring During Drain',
  '### Watch Lease Transfers

```sql
-- Monitor lease count decreasing on draining node
SELECT node_id, leases
FROM crdb_internal.kv_store_status
WHERE node_id = 3;
```

**Expected**: Leases drop to 0 within seconds.

### Check Active Sessions

```sql
-- Monitor active SQL sessions on draining node
SELECT session_id, user_name, application_name, active_queries
FROM crdb_internal.cluster_sessions
WHERE node_id = 3;
```

**Expected**: Sessions decrease to 0 as connections close naturally.

### View Drain Progress in Logs

```bash
# Watch drain progress in logs
tail -f /var/log/cockroach/cockroach.log | grep -i drain
```

**Key log messages:**
```
I260307 14:23:10.123 server/drain.go:123 ⋮ drain requested
I260307 14:23:10.234 server/drain.go:234 ⋮ beginning unready phase
I260307 14:23:10.345 server/drain.go:345 ⋮ transferring leases
I260307 14:23:15.456 server/drain.go:456 ⋮ all leases transferred
I260307 14:23:15.567 server/drain.go:567 ⋮ waiting for SQL connections to close
I260307 14:24:22.678 server/drain.go:678 ⋮ drain complete
```',
  6,
