INSERT INTO chunks (id, skill_id, section_title, content, chunk_index, embedding) VALUES (
  '59b7be7a-5408-5c1a-b033-b7a1773a8a2b',
  '367b6ffc-261d-5fd7-8f05-fd29fb08aa19',
  'Step 1: Configure Drain Settings',
  'Set appropriate drain timeouts for rolling restart.

### Standard Configuration

```sql
-- Connect to any node
cockroach sql --certs-dir=certs --host=<any-node>:26257

-- Configure drain settings
SET CLUSTER SETTING server.shutdown.initial_wait = ''8s'';
SET CLUSTER SETTING server.shutdown.connections.timeout = ''15s'';
SET CLUSTER SETTING server.shutdown.transactions.timeout = ''30s'';

-- Verify settings
SHOW CLUSTER SETTING server.shutdown.initial_wait;
SHOW CLUSTER SETTING server.shutdown.connections.timeout;
SHOW CLUSTER SETTING server.shutdown.transactions.timeout;
```

**Why These Values**:
- `initial_wait = 8s`: Time for load balancer health checks to fail (2s interval × 3 failures + buffer)
- `connections.timeout = 15s`: Time for idle connections to close
- `transactions.timeout = 30s`: Time for queries to complete (adjust for your workload)

---

### For Long-Running Queries

```sql
-- If cluster has analytical/batch queries
SET CLUSTER SETTING server.shutdown.transactions.timeout = ''2m'';
```

