- [ ] Zero under-replicated ranges
- [ ] Zero unavailable ranges
- [ ] All nodes at same version (for upgrades)
- [ ] SQL connectivity works on all nodes
- [ ] Load balancer shows all nodes UP
- [ ] Application metrics normal
- [ ] No increase in error rates

