INSERT INTO chunks (id, skill_id, section_title, content, chunk_index, embedding) VALUES (
  'a4dfa58d-abb3-586f-9522-75ff8de918ae',
  '367b6ffc-261d-5fd7-8f05-fd29fb08aa19',
  'CockroachDB v26.1 Notes',
  '### Rolling Upgrade Support

v26.1 supports rolling upgrades from v26.0:
- Nodes can run mixed versions temporarily
- Use `cluster.preserve_downgrade_option` to prevent auto-finalization
- Test thoroughly before finalizing
- Finalize by resetting preserve downgrade option

```sql
-- Before upgrade
SET CLUSTER SETTING cluster.preserve_downgrade_option = ''26.0'';

-- After all nodes upgraded and tested
RESET CLUSTER SETTING cluster.preserve_downgrade_option;
```

### Drain Command (v26.1)

**Current Method**:
```bash
cockroach node drain <node_id> --host=<node>:26257
```

**Deprecated Method**:
```bash
cockroach quit --decommission=false  # Don''t use
```

### Health Check Integration

v26.1 fully integrates drain with health checks:
- `/health?ready=1` returns 503 immediately when drain starts
- Load balancers automatically remove node
- No manual intervention needed (if configured correctly)

