INSERT INTO chunks (id, skill_id, section_title, content, chunk_index, embedding) VALUES (
  '563b70bb-6522-532b-a744-8fe870ec4826',
  '2a590116-b715-573c-a481-c647d9b0488e',
  'Setting preserve_downgrade_option',
  '### Why Set This First

**Purpose**: Prevent automatic version finalization

**Allows**:
- Time to test new version
- Rollback if issues discovered
- Manual control of finalization

### Set Before Upgrade

```sql
-- Connect to any node
cockroach sql --certs-dir=certs

-- Set to current version
SET CLUSTER SETTING cluster.preserve_downgrade_option = ''25.2'';
```

**Verify**:
```sql
SHOW CLUSTER SETTING cluster.preserve_downgrade_option;
-- Should show: 25.2
```

**Important**: Set to CURRENT version (not target version)',
