INSERT INTO chunks (id, skill_id, section_title, content, chunk_index, embedding) VALUES (
  '6e2c23b1-541d-5d13-87e8-ad917d5317ce',
  '2a590116-b715-573c-a481-c647d9b0488e',
  'When to Finalize',
  '### Wait Period Recommendations

**Minimum**: 24 hours on new version
**Recommended**: 48-72 hours
**Conservative**: 1 week

**Finalize when**:
- ✅ All tests passing
- ✅ No unexpected errors
- ✅ Performance acceptable
- ✅ Confident in upgrade success

### How to Finalize

See `finalize-cluster-version-upgrades` and `manage-version-finalization` skills',
  9,
