INSERT INTO chunks (id, skill_id, section_title, content, chunk_index, embedding) VALUES (
  '5babd2d7-c6f4-5a10-b268-b4a7bbd74546',
  'e9cac7bf-e348-5101-9f82-c6970c0fe034',
  'Basic PITR Syntax',
  '### Restore to Specific Timestamp

```sql
-- Restore database to exact point in time
RESTORE DATABASE mydb
  FROM LATEST IN ''nodelocal://1/backups/pitr''
  AS OF SYSTEM TIME ''2026-03-05 10:14:00''
  WITH new_db_name = ''mydb_recovered'';
```

**Components**:
- `RESTORE DATABASE mydb` - What to restore
- `FROM LATEST IN` - Use most recent backup chain
- `AS OF SYSTEM TIME` - The magic: restore to this exact time
- `WITH new_db_name` - Restore alongside original (not replace)

### Restore to Relative Timestamp

```sql
-- Restore to 1 hour ago
RESTORE DATABASE mydb
  FROM LATEST IN ''nodelocal://1/backups/pitr''
  AS OF SYSTEM TIME ''-1h''
  WITH new_db_name = ''mydb_1h_ago'';
```

**Relative time formats**:
- `''-1h''` - 1 hour ago
- `''-30m''` - 30 minutes ago
- `''-2h30m''` - 2.5 hours ago
- `''-10s''` - 10 seconds ago',
