  'b877e695-432f-59e7-9b09-4bc85b7b5a90',
  'e9cac7bf-e348-5101-9f82-c6970c0fe034',
  'Key Takeaways',
  '1. **PITR enables time travel** to any point in the past
2. **Requires revision_history backups** to work
3. **Bounded by GC TTL** - can''t go back further than GC window
4. **Restore to new database** to validate before replacing
5. **Perfect for logical errors** (accidental deletes, bad updates)
6. **Test regularly** to ensure PITR works when needed',
  9,
