INSERT INTO chunks (id, skill_id, section_title, content, chunk_index, embedding) VALUES (
  'dc1302c2-5e25-5ecd-ad35-222adb2f708c',
  '68d4e21c-7c04-59ad-b8a0-bec37d9d0149',
  'Verify Schedule Created',
  '```sql
-- List all schedules
SHOW SCHEDULES;

-- Find specific schedule by name
SELECT * FROM [SHOW SCHEDULES]
WHERE schedule_name LIKE ''%Production%'';
```

**Check**:
- `schedule_status`: Should be ''ACTIVE''
- `next_run`: Shows next execution time
