  '4de694d4-f14e-5061-9f6e-a08b6a73620d',
  '28b0c72a-66db-5949-b183-d2052b669bbf',
  'What This Skill Teaches',
  'You''ll understand:
- How **voting replicas** participate in Raft consensus to achieve write quorum
- How **non-voting replicas** provide fast local reads without impacting write latency
- Why GLOBAL tables use non-voting replicas for scalability
- How quorum calculation changes with mixed replica types
- When CockroachDB automatically creates non-voting replicas
- The limitations of non-voting replicas (cannot hold write leases)',
