INSERT INTO chunks (id, skill_id, section_title, content, chunk_index, embedding) VALUES (
  '77214242-ba0e-5b08-95e8-f34193291463',
  'b3f1b347-c49c-5ab3-9435-6bc964710599',
  'Visualizing Leaseholder Architecture',
  '### Single-Region Deployment

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Region: us-east                                              │
│                                                              │
│  ┌─────────┐       ┌─────────┐       ┌─────────┐           │
│  │ Node 1  │       │ Node 2  │       │ Node 3  │           │
│  │         │       │         │       │         │           │
│  │ Range 1 │       │ Range 1 │       │ Range 1 │           │
│  │ LEASE   │◄──────┤ Replica │◄──────┤ Replica │           │
│  │ HOLDER  │ Raft  │         │ Raft  │         │           │
│  └─────────┘       └─────────┘       └─────────┘           │
│       ▲                                                      │
│       │                                                      │
│       └─── All reads served here (local, ~5ms)              │
│            Writes fast (~15ms with local Raft)              │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Multi-Region Deployment (REGIONAL BY TABLE)

```
┌──────────────────┐  ┌──────────────────┐  ┌──────────────────┐
│ Region: us-east  │  │ Region: us-west  │  │ Region: eu-west  │
│                  │  │                  │  │                  │
│  ┌────────────┐  │  │  ┌────────────┐  │  │  ┌────────────┐  │
│  │  Node 1    │  │  │  │  Node 2    │  │  │  │  Node 3    │  │
│  │            │  │  │  │            │  │  │  │            │  │
│  │  Range 1   │  │  │  │  Range 1   │  │  │  │  Range 1   │  │
│  │  LEASE     │◄─┼──┼──┤  Replica   │◄─┼──┼──┤  Replica   │  │
│  │  HOLDER    │  │  │  │            │  │  │  │            │  │
│  │  (users)   │  │  │  │            │  │  │  │            │  │
│  └────────────┘  │  │  └────────────┘  │  │  └────────────┘  │
│        ▲         │  │                  │  │                  │
│        │         │  │                  │  │                  │
│  Reads from      │  │ Reads from       │  │ Reads from       │
│  us-east: 5ms    │  │ us-west: 75ms    │  │ eu-west: 150ms   │
└──────────────────┘  └──────────────────┘  └──────────────────┘

Table: users SET LOCALITY REGIONAL BY TABLE IN "us-east"
Result: Fast reads from us-east, slow from other regions
```

### Multi-Region Deployment (REGIONAL BY ROW)

Each row''s leaseholder placed in the row''s home region (stored in `crdb_region` column):

```
us-east: Range 1 leaseholder (rows with region=''us-east'')
us-west: Range 2 leaseholder (rows with region=''us-west'')
eu-west: Range 3 leaseholder (rows with region=''eu-west'')

Result: Each row gets local-latency reads from its home region
```',
